msgid "Abstaining from Fornication and Other Acts of Sexual Immorality"
msgstr "Zich onthouden van hoererij en andere daden van seksuele immoraliteit"

#: walkasjesus_app.dynamic/law_of_messiah
msgid "Accepting Suffering and Disgrace in Order to Serve Yeshua"
msgstr "Lijden en schande aanvaarden om Yeshua te dienen"

#: walkasjesus_app.dynamic/law_of_messiah
msgid "Accompanying Our Faith with Actions"
msgstr "Ons geloof begeleiden met daden"

