#: walkasjesus_app.dynamic/law_of_messiah
msgid "Acknowledging Yeshua as Our Spiritual Leader"
msgstr "Erkenning van Yeshua als onze geestelijke leider"

#: walkasjesus_app.dynamic/law_of_messiah
msgid "Acknowledging and not Denying Belief in God and in Yeshua"
